":"dba28e57e2255ae3feab80fb64fea6b0d8ba3019","tid":680181,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61afc9f22f679ee81d0f0e382adab5898925a731","tid":680181,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"no house=slave"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"so u = slave"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1993d037d8982080be03547705393f691a97e953","tid":680181,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"其實係馬克思d左翼撚先成日將階級對立<br />\n但實際上，特別係中國呢d，一般嘅農民係可以靠自己耕田之後儲錢，然後慢慢晉升為富農，階級之間係有流動性"},{"pid":"a5fb59d79e4b2453abb1b20beeea9df657dc5186","tid":680181,"uid":146146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"你睇番二千幾年前羅馬, 有地既一樣係貴族, 其實從來都無變過。<br />\n<br />\n有地既貴族好難先會跌落平民, 幾千年來一直都係咁玩, 只要無資產係手, 一世都係平民。<br />\n<br />\n就算平民起義, 都只係會多左班新貴族(出來嘈得最大聲果班), 其他既咪一樣係做平民。"},{"pid":"fe301689cb327887e3e66d577e0053ee7017b423","tid":680181,"uid":68556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"你估業主咁易做。<br />\n供樓又要捱貴利息，每季差餉地租，每月管理費，定期維修;<br />\n又要幾十年節衣縮食，無得去旅行，fine dining，無生活態度，<br />\n又要驚失業，有病斷供;<br />\n又要驚樓爆做負資產，俾銀行call loan;<br />\n又要俾人笑做樓奴。<br />\n<br />\n租樓就調轉可以日日賺，<br />\n唔會病唔會失業，<br />\n可以笑人做樓奴，<br />\n又可以投資用股息交租做股神，<br />\n我好羨慕呀。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d439f07e2bef1a836898217b77773da6349e9e","tid":680181,"uid":45582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe301689cb327887e3e66d577e0053ee7017b423","tid":680181,"uid":68556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"你估業主咁易做。<br />\n供樓又要捱貴利息，每季差餉地租，每月管理費，定期維修;<br />\n又要幾十年節衣縮食，無得去旅行，fine dining，無生活態度，<br />\n又要驚失業，有病斷供;<br />\n又要驚樓爆做負資產，俾銀行call loan;<br />\n又要俾人笑做樓奴。<br />\n<br />\n租樓就調轉可以日日賺，<br />\n唔會病唔會失業，<br />\n可以笑人做樓奴，<br />\n又可以投資用股息交租做股神，<br />\n我好羨慕呀。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"講真。<br />\n近年黎講08至13年做業主都同14至18年做工業主果堆好唔同啦。<br />\ncall loan樓爆有排未到13年前業主。<br />\n<br />\n但租客就陰公豬, 唔租勁細單位都儲唔到錢做首期。"},{"pid":"05e013c5b364abbb89056e859eeed6d763129f6d","tid":680181,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:47:34.000Z","msg":"頭先睇完70年代 V型電磁俠有感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n（勁似有樓、冇樓者之戰）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/125943_ed823d844792987c32e8553c484605f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F125943_ed823d844792987c32e8553c484605f4.png&h=3b66108f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/125947_75fa23b413d16ed5b3c4144007f9364c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F125947_75fa23b413d16ed5b3c4144007f9364c.png&h=0200fbe8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/125949_7be21d490ac05dd5825fe26efdbc4b69.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F125949_7be21d490ac05dd5825fe26efdbc4b69.png&h=803f1c88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/125950_bbbfbb68972ca1231485f86d47c7c34b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F125950_bbbfbb68972ca1231485f86d47c7c34b.png&h=ec53e546&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a54962ba9f7b472ba94a3f9534848a07a17fa561","tid":680181,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:30:58.000Z","msg